╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║        🎮 NOBARA OS – GAMING SYSTEM SETUP REFERENCE         ║
║       Replicate these settings to build your own distro     ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

1️⃣  PERFORMANCE TUNING (Kernel & Drivers)
────────────────────────────────────────────
✔ Custom kernel patches (based on Fedora kernel)
✔ FSR (FidelityFX Super Resolution) global support
✔ Tweakable TDP/fan controls (Steam Deck / AMD platforms)
✔ Latest Mesa drivers + Vulkan RADV backend
✔ Full support for AMD Radeon 600M/700M iGPUs (like 680M, 780M)
✔ Enabled zram swap (compressed RAM)

2️⃣  CORE GAMING PACKAGES
────────────────────────────────────────────
✔ Steam (Native or Flatpak)
✔ Lutris
✔ Proton-GE (via ProtonUp-Qt or system install)
✔ Wine-GE & Wine-Staging
✔ DXVK, VKD3D, and all dependencies preinstalled
✔ GameMode – auto CPU governor switcher
✔ Gamescope – game session compositor
✔ MangoHud – performance overlay
✔ vkBasalt – post-processing effects (e.g., sharpening)
✔ GOverlay – GUI for MangoHud & vkBasalt

3️⃣  CREATIVE TOOLS (optional)
────────────────────────────────────────────
✔ OBS Studio + Browser Plugin (for streaming)
✔ Kdenlive (video editing)
✔ Blender (3D modeling)
✔ DaVinci Resolve (setup wizard included)
✔ Audacity (audio editing)

4️⃣  SYSTEM UTILITIES
────────────────────────────────────────────
✔ CoreCtrl – power profiles (CPU/GPU tuning)
✔ Flatseal – manage Flatpak permissions
✔ Flatpak + Flathub + Flatpost (GUI app manager)
✔ Nobara Driver Manager – auto detect proprietary drivers
✔ Nobara Package Manager (yumex + bauh)
✔ GNOME or KDE Tweaks tool
✔ Discord Canary (Flatpak)
✔ Microsoft Fonts preinstalled (for Wine UI compatibility)

5️⃣  PERFORMANCE SETTINGS & POLICIES
────────────────────────────────────────────
✔ GameMode autostarts with Steam & Lutris games
✔ Global MangoHud overlay with custom toggle
✔ Per-app GameMode toggle supported
✔ Filesystem tweaks for shader cache performance
✔ Latest Proton & Wine prefixes configured via user tools
✔ Optional: real-time audio support (low-latency gaming)

6️⃣  OPTIONAL: GAMING UI SHELL (Steam Deck Mode)
────────────────────────────────────────────
✔ Steam Deck UI mode available via session switch
✔ Gamescope integrated with Deck-style window management

╔═════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║     To replicate on other distros:          ║
╠═════════════════════════════════════════════╣
║ - Use Flatpak or APT/Pacman/DNF versions    ║
║ - Install GameMode, MangoHud, vkBasalt      ║
║ - Use ProtonUp-Qt for Proton-GE/Wine-GE     ║
║ - Add zram, install CoreCtrl                ║
║ - Set kernel boot params (FSR, perf)        ║
║ - Configure Flatseal for Steam/Lutris       ║
╚═════════════════════════════════════════════╝

✅ Recommended Base Distros:
  - Fedora Kinoite / Workstation (RPM-based)
  - Ubuntu Minimal or Server + Flatpaks
  - Arch / EndeavourOS / Garuda (for rolling users)
  
